## Entry & bootstrap

- `lib/main.dart`: `WidgetsFlutterBinding` → load `ThemeSettings` → `initSupabase()` → `profileRoleNotifier` if session → auth listener → `FcmService.init()` → `ProviderScope` + `MaterialApp.router` (`appRouter`, theme from `themeSettingsProvider`).

