## Student ID policy (current)

- Canonical student ID format: **`RCC` + last 9 digits of phone**.
- Enforced in DB via trigger/function migration (`20260410143000_student_id_rcc_last9_and_results_leaderboard_rls.sql`).
- Keep app-side assumptions aligned with this rule (do not reintroduce year-based IDs).

