## Architecture

- **Repositories** own all Supabase I/O; screens/widgets call repositories or Riverpod providers.
- Prefer **ConsumerWidget** / **ConsumerStatefulWidget** when using `ref`.
- Table names: **`kTable*`** in `lib/core/constants.dart` — keep in sync with migrations.

